snippet.title: The Infographics Show
snippet.description:
Facts are fun, but most are presented in boring and badly edited videos. The Infographics Show focuses on making animated motion infographic videos, made in a fun and entertaining way. 

Software that we use: Adobe Audition for voice recording, Adobe Illustrator for dealing with vectors, and Adobe After Effects for animation. 

If you want to sponsor a video or discuss any other business-related things, you can get our email below.

sl_SI.title: Infografična oddaja
sl_SI.description: Dejstva so zabavna ampak ponavadi so predstavljena zelo dolgočasno. Infografična oddaja ustvarja infografične videje na zabaven in zanimiv način.
